file.name: Preview.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
Preview:
  type: object
  description: |
    Use this object to enable the Preview mode in the request.
    Use the Preview mode to test the look and feel of your site for various location and offer combinations.

  properties:
    token:
      type: string
      description: |
        The token for the Preview mode.
        Validation
          * Verify that the token belongs to the client provided in request.
